name: Aaron Locatis
bio: I got into computer coding because I drastically wanted a career change. I was inspired by my brother, who had done this exact same scenario 5 years prior. He has had great success in his career and is now a senior developer here in Omaha. I would like to eventually fit into a great company where I can contribute to a positive working environment and be a valueable asset with good work/life balance.
